(55, 1, '1', '3', '20', 'All new Echo Show 5 (2nd Gen, 2021 release) - Smart speaker with 5.5\"(13.9cm) screen, crisp sound and Alexa (Blue)', 'all-new-echo-show-5-2nd-gen-2021-release---smart-speaker-with-55139cm-screen-crisp-sound-and-alexa-blue', '10', NULL, NULL, 'pc', 'uploads/1674025486.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, '8999', '0', '8000', 'flat', '999', '0.00', '30', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: #0f1111; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Echo Show 5 is a smart speaker with 5.5&rdquo; screen and Alexa that can be operated by voice and can fit on your bedside or coffee table. Alexa speaks English &amp; Hindi.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Hands-free music control: Stream millions of songs in your favorite language from Amazon Prime Music, Spotify, JioSaavn, Gaana, and Apple Music. Enjoy singing along with on screen lyrics from Amazon Prime Music.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Your personal entertainment corner: Watch your favorite movies and TV shows from Amazon Prime Video and Netflix.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Monitor your home remotely: Activate the built-in camera remotely to securely monitor your home using the Alexa app.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Get started with Smart home: Setup smart lights, plugs or cameras with Echo Show 5 and control your appliances using just voice.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Improved 2MP camera: Use the 2 MP camera to call friends and family who have the Alexa app or Echo Show devices. Use drop-in feature to check on your kids or parents &ndash; just like an intercom.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Manage your day better:Just ask Alexa to set reminders and timers. Watch the latest news or get weather updates while you are rushing through your daily chores.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Designed to protect your privacy - Comes with a mic off button and a built-in camera cover.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<div class=\"content-grid-row-wrapper lazy-loading-background-image lazy-loading-background-color\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; margin: 0px auto; background-size: cover; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; color: #ffffff; min-height: 864px; max-width: 1504px; background-image: url(\'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/31/kindle/journeys/2FTxq92FDulmt3Q9KXNExiZJ9DxFx4VY4ayn2mqBLyL0k3D/Y2M5NWQ2NmMt\');\" data-lazy-loading-background-image=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/31/kindle/journeys/2FTxq92FDulmt3Q9KXNExiZJ9DxFx4VY4ayn2mqBLyL0k3D/Y2M5NWQ2NmMt\">\r\n<div class=\"a-row\" style=\